description: Chic and modern, the Alice Top was designed to be a closet staple. Featuring a slightly cropped and relaxed fit, this piece shows off your shape while still being comfortable. Pair back to the Phyllis Wrap Skirt for a coordinated look.

This elegant Neckerchief is crafted from high-quality silk, providing a luxurious and soft feel against the skin. Its versatile size and stylish design make it a perfect accessory to elevate any outfit, adding a touch of sophistication and refinement. The Neckerchief's lightweight and flexible fabric allow it to be worn as a chic hair accessory or a classic neck scarf, making it a versatile addition to any fashion-forward wardrobe. Print by Danika Herrick.

Featuring our Signature Fall Floral that's reminiscent of a traditional block print with a beautiful watercolor background.
